---
title: Garlicky Shrimp Couscous Bowls with Chili-Roasted Broccoli & Fresh Parsley
description: Bowls are a go-to meal when we’re in the mood for creative lunch and dinner ideas. Why? It’s simple: everything’s better in a bowl! This quick, fresh rendition is a great way to meet your summer goals (including getting back outside more quickly!). You’ll top garlic, lemon, and parsley-scented Israeli couscous with quick-cooking garlicky shrimp, chili-roasted broccoli, and a rich drizzle of delicious lemon-butter sauce. One bite = totally bowled over.
